The following program consists of 3 concurrent processes and 3 binary semaphores. The semaphores are initialized as S0 = 1, S1 = 0, S2 = 0.

Process P0
while(true)
{
    wait(S0);
    print '0';
    release(S1);
    release(S2);
}

Process P1
wait(S1);
release(S0);

Process P2
wait(S2);
release(S0);

---
How many times will P0 print '0'?

